---
// SocietyBar.astro
// Small shared footer strip tying every AGI-26 property back to the wider
// Society of Minds Aligned. Self-contained styling (no Tailwind/CSS-var
// dependency) so it renders consistently across both site families in this
// monorepo. Added 2026-07-17 (Dee) per Mike's cross-linking directive.
// 2026-07-22: SOMA 2026 leads the strip — it is the canonical "what this is and why"
// page for the constellation, and every property must reach it in one click.
---

<footer class="society-bar">
  <p class="society-bar__text">
    Part of the <strong>Society of Minds Aligned</strong> —
    <a href="https://agi2026.netlify.app/soma2026/" class="society-bar__lead">SOMA 2026</a>
    <span class="society-bar__sep">·</span>
    <a href="https://minds-aligned-door.netlify.app">Minds Aligned</a>
    <span class="society-bar__sep">·</span>
    <a href="https://siliconchildren.com">Silicon Children</a>
    <span class="society-bar__sep">·</span>
    <a href="https://minds-at-work-soma.netlify.app">Minds at Work</a>
  </p>
</footer>

<style>
  .society-bar {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    background: #0a0f1a;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .society-bar__text {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #9ba3b5;
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  }

  .society-bar__text strong {
    color: #e9eaed;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .society-bar__sep {
    margin: 0 0.35rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .society-bar a {
    color: #6f9bff;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .society-bar a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .society-bar__lead {
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
